            <title>[SOLR-17641] Disable security manager when Java &gt;=24 detected</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17641</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The main thing here is to disable the Security Manager for Java 24+, both for the CLI and testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reference: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/lucene/issues/14184&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/lucene/issues/14184&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
